Camera-based EyeWriter implementation

Tested on oFv007, and requires following addons:
https://github.com/kylemcdonald/ofxCv
https://github.com/kylemcdonald/ofxFaceTracker
You need to place the model data of the face tracker in "bin/data/model/".

